{"tid":725153,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有關賭波既數學問題","createTime":"2018-07-01T13:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T14:25:43.000Z","uid":57346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cf1d1cfa63e96e5465a9b8da68ac16616803831e","tid":725153,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T13:58:57.000Z","msg":"我個fd最近賭波輸左一萬蚊<br />\n我睇返佢d飛<br />\n佢多數買8場過關<br />\n10蚊注但串埋好多場<br />\n張張飛要千幾二千蚊<br />\n<br />\n其實數學上<br />\n依種投注方式係咪好蠢？<br />\n<br />\n例如：佢用十注去買一場，最多中一注，啫係有九注必定唔中。<br />\n<br />\n不如十注買十場？係咪咁？<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔賭錢+數學攞D"},{"pid":"5a1e5097d9c479d46a0c54c4a58aa83147214bb0","tid":725153,"uid":108090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:01:08.000Z","msg":"喺香港馬會賭已經on9"},{"pid":"6a80d270797bf7528b038fdb5cf3f50d09b503e4","tid":725153,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bde6cd6a2bdf546dab7d3381931da064aeaea2b","tid":725153,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a80d270797bf7528b038fdb5cf3f50d09b503e4","tid":725153,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:03:35.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講解下？<br />\n<br />\n我其實係想問4串3～4串7～8串10果類野！<br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔知咩意思！"},{"pid":"99d0853936a29f4551e30849f0dff766022aa315","tid":725153,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c0a90655193b39ccc649ad8a6d281cdaf6c82ab","tid":725153,"uid":100760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:12:02.000Z","msg":"賭得就一定輸"},{"pid":"e8ae35320690657dd67736752111c31f22442a7b","tid":725153,"uid":57346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf1d1cfa63e96e5465a9b8da68ac16616803831e","tid":725153,"uid":57346